(1, 1, 'Shiksha Sagar', 'RakshaKids Mobile App Download', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n	<title>Raksha Kids</title>\n	\n</head>\n<body>\n	<div style = "max-width: 500px;\n		background: #eeeeee;\n		padding:10px;\n		margin: 0px auto;\n		overflow: hidden;\n		border-radius:5px;\n		font-family:sans-serif;">\n	<img style="max-width: 100%;width:70px;height:70px;padding-left:40%;" src = "http://35.160.140.119/rk/images/icon.png" align= "middle">\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">\n	Dear Parents,<br><br>\n	Greetings!<br>\n	We are looking forward to introducing you to our new application called Raksha Kids.<br>\n	Raksha Kids is developed for the protection of kids while they travel to school and on their way back home.<br>\n	Here,the parents will get notified when kids check in & out from the school through Raksha Kids mobile app.<br><br/>\n	How Does the Technology Work?<br><br>\n	1. A smart card will be provided to the student and this card will be connected to the parent''s mobile. \n	When the student enters or exits the school gate, the student has to show the card to the device placed at the school gate.\n	<br>\n	2. You will receive the notification through our application (<a href = "http://www.poornaapp.com/raksha-kids/">Raksha Kids</a>). \n	<br>\n	3. Raksha Kids will give the information about the student''s entry and exit from the school.\n	Also you will be receiving all the updates from the school regarding holidays, time table, diary etc.<br><br>\n	\n	We are happy to inform you that we are tied up with Shiksha Sagar School in this mission.<br><br>\n	We would like you to download our app and start using with the following email and passcode and enjoy the facilities provided.<br><br>\n	Email: [email]<br>\n	Passcode:[passcode]<br>\n	</p>\n	<div style = "text-align:center;margin:20px;">\n	<a style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;background:#03A99A;color:white;padding:10px 20px 10px" href = "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.poornaapp.rakshakids">Click here to download the app</a>\n	</div>\n	<div class = "contact">\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">For more information visit: <a href = "http://www.poornaapp.com/">http://www.poornaapp.com/</a></p>\n	</div>\n</body>\n</html>', NULL, '', '2016-10-21 08:11:33', '2016-10-21 08:11:33', 1),
(2, 1, 'Shiksha Sagar Reminder', 'RakshaKids Mobile App Download', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n	<title>Raksha Kids</title>\n	\n</head>\n<body>\n	<div style = "max-width: 500px;\n		background: #eeeeee;\n		padding:10px;\n		margin: 0px auto;\n		overflow: hidden;\n		border-radius:5px;\n		font-family:sans-serif;">\n	<img style="max-width: 100%;width:70px;height:70px;padding-left:40%;" src = "http://35.160.140.119/rk/images/icon.png" align= "middle">\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">\n\n	Dear Parent,<br><br>\n	Greetings!<br><br>\n	Raksha Kids once again advice all parents to download <b>Raksha Kids App</b>.<br>\n	If you have missed our previous mail by any chance, kindly follow the instructions given below and download the application.<br>\n\n	Raksha Kids is developed for the protection of kids while they travel to school and on their way back home.<br><br>\n	<!-- Together let us work on the protecion of your child<br><br> -->\n	<b>Benefits of Raksha Kids</b><br><br>\n	The smartcard which has been provided your child will now help you monitor and safeguard your child and check attendance, messages / notes, timetable etc from school.<br>\n\n	Parents are advised to please check our app regularly for instructions and updates about your child from school.<br><br>\n	 \n\n	Let us together work on this mission.<br>\n	So we would like you to download our app and start using it with the following email and passcode and enjoy the facilities provided.\n	<br>\n	<br>\n	We would like you to download our app and start using with the following email and passcode and enjoy the facilities provided.<br><br>\n	Email: [email]<br>\n	Passcode:[passcode]<br>\n	</p>\n	\n	<div style = "text-align:center;margin:20px;">\n	<a style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;background:#03A99A;color:white;padding:10px 20px 10px" href = "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.poornaapp.rakshakids">Click here to download the app</a>\n	</div>\n	<div class = "contact">\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">For more information visit: <a href = "http://www.poornaapp.com/rakshakids">http://www.poornaapp.com/rakshakids</a></p>\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">Contact us on: <br>\n	Email:&nbsp;<a id="contact_mobile" href="mailto:contact@poornaapp.com">contact@poornaapp.com</a><br>\n	Phone:&nbsp;<a id="contact_email" href="tel:080-40923665">080-40923665</a></p>\n	</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 'Dear+Parent,Kindly+download+the+Raksha+kids+app+on+your+smartphone.+Details+of+the+setup+is+sent+to+your+registered+email+id.+-+Raksha+kids.', ' ', '2017-03-02 00:00:00', '2017-03-02 00:00:00', 1),
(3, NULL, 'Registration Confirmation', 'Registration Confirmation', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n	<title>Raksha Kids</title>\n	<style>\n	p\n	{\n		font-family:Times New Roman;\n		margin:20px;\n		font-size:14px;\n	}\n	</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n	<div style = "max-width: 500px;\n		background: #eeeeee;\n		padding:10px;\n		margin: 0px auto;\n		overflow: hidden;\n		border-radius:5px;\n		font-family:sans-serif;">\n	<img style="max-width: 100%;width:70px;height:70px;padding-left:40%;" src = "http://35.160.140.119/rk/images/icon.png" align= "middle"><br>\n	<p style="float: right; max-width:200px; word-wrap:break-word"><b>School Name:</b> [schoolName] <br> <b>Date:</b>[date]</p><br><br>\n	<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;margin:20px;font-size:14px;">\n	\n	Dear Sir/Madam, <br><br>\n	You are welcome! <br><br>\n	Thank you for registering with us. For moving forward kindly send us the details of total no. of schools and the total strength in each class, etc. We also welcome every parent and their child, regardless of background or ability. Parents can enroll their child in the regular program at your designated school. \n	<br>\n	<br>\n	Parents have to register their child details into our website and they can <a href = "https://www.rakshakids.com/rk/schoolregister/register.html?id=[SchoolIdName]">https://www.rakshakids.com/rk/schoolregister/register.html?id=[SchoolIdName]</a> to proceed or they can copy and paste the complete URL into the address bar to enroll their child. They can refer the attachment for more details.<br><br/>\n	\n	Once the parents have registered their kids into your school, you can conform or reject the child. The separate link will be provided for this. Kindly <a href = "https://www.rakshakids.com/rk/schoolregister/">https://www.rakshakids.com/rk/schoolregister</a> to proceed or you can copy and paste the complete URL into the address bar to conform or reject the child. Kindly use the below credentials.\n	<br><br>\n	User Name: [email]<br>\n	Passcod